y first communion. And, at nine, I joined the religion of Umbanda. <br>\n<br>\nI pray the Catholic prayers, just like in church, and then we go to Umbanda. Even in Candomblé and Umbanda he is the son of Xangô. As long as I live and he lives, the faith in the rosary will be strengthened.</p>"
